data.value:
Choose load a template if you want to load the previous session configuration file.
Choose a security setting if you want to go through security configurations.
Choose Lock down if you want to harden your security.
Choose "All setting" if you want to do both security setting and lock down configurations.

data.name: label110.Text
data.value:
Congratulations!
The configuration is complete.
If you chose to store passwords in the logbook file, we advise you to save the logbook file to a secure location.
Click "Save log" to save logbook file on a different location.
